Jonathan Harker is a solicitor, or lawyer, whose firm sends him to Transylvania to conclude a real estate transaction with Dracula. Young and na√Øve, Harker quickly finds himself a prisoner in the castle and barely escapes with his life. He demonstrates a fierce curiosity to discover the true nature of his captor and a strong will to escape. Later, after becoming convinced that the count has moved to London, Harker emerges as a brave and fearless fighter.